## API calls

Add endpoints to `store/api/index.ts` (or split modules like `store/api/admin.ts`). Use tag invalidation for cache:

```typescript
updateSettings: builder.mutation<void, { serverId: string; settings: Partial<ISettings> }>({
  query: ({ serverId, settings }) => ({
    url: `/servers/${serverId}/settings`,
    method: "PUT",
    body: settings,
  }),
  invalidatesTags: ["Server"],
}),
```

Base URL: `REACT_APP_API_URL` (defaults to `/api`).

## Components

- Functional components with typed props interfaces (`IPageProps`, `PageProps`)
- Prefer RTK Query hooks (`useFetchServerQuery`) over ad-hoc fetch
- Avoid `any` — define or extend types in `types/`
- Before finishing, run in the dashboard container: `ctl exec dashboard npm run lint`, `ctl exec dashboard npx tsc --noEmit`, and `ctl exec dashboard npm run prettier` (see project overview for full `ctl` usage)
